description:
This Coding Challenge is a follow up on the challenge #54.1: Islamic Star Patterns. In this video, I use the Law of Sines to simplify the tiling pattern calculation. In honor of my 200,000th subscriber I am donating $200 to each of the 4 charities mentioned below. Thanks to all of you for watching and your support!!
